419
00:20:52.260 --> 00:20:55.580
Drowning Prevention Auckland strongly supports that direction.

420
00:20:57.160 --> 00:21:00.860
However, we believe the remaining issue is the proposed threshold of

421
00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:03.800
