422
00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:08.570
Our concern is that vessel length does not reflect how drowning

423
00:21:08.660 --> 00:21:11.760
risk actually occurs. People

424
00:21:11.880 --> 00:21:15.620
unexpectedly enter the water from vessels of all sizes

425
00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:19.220
through falls overboard, capsizing, collisions,

426
00:21:19.700 --> 00:21:22.900
bar crossings, rough conditions, or medical events.

427
00:21:23.740 --> 00:21:27.380
The evidence shows a substantial proportion of recreational boating

428
00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:31.000
activity incidents and fatalities involve vessels

429
00:21:31.020 --> 00:21:32.400
