432
00:21:41.150 --> 00:21:42.260
public safety rule.

433
00:21:43.650 --> 00:21:47.359
Most recreational boaties do not know their vessel's waterline length.

434
00:21:47.400 --> 00:21:50.400
They know the advertised or overall length of their boat.

435
00:21:51.260 --> 00:21:54.980
Introducing a technical measurement that is not currently used within

436
00:21:55.060 --> 00:21:59.020
Maritime Rule Part 91 risks confusion for both

437
00:21:59.040 --> 00:22:01.120
