440
00:22:09.920 --> 00:22:13.340
If the vessel is underway, the lifejacket is worn.

441
00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:18.280
I'll now invite Dr. Teresa Stanley to briefly speak to the human

442
00:22:18.320 --> 00:22:21.640
